		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Is there anyone who recognizes this weirdness I've discovered about the Four Score adapters I own? (I have two of them now since I erroneously thought my old one had broken and bought myself another one)
<br />
<br />I own no less than 8 NES controllers, and out of these, no more than 3 will work with a Four Score adapter. What gives?

		

